{"data":[{"date":"20:42 14/08","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Olympic Pakistan qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 5-0 n\u1ebfu C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 penalty l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD 2018 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Pakistan sau 3 n\u0103m c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf do \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb FIFA. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/39153073_314524165961734_1198343060094713856_n-500-1534240172-977-width500height333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t r\u1ee1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng&hellip; nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i chung Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c xa v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 cao c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Olympic Pakistan song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. D\u1eabu sao nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/39183757_383787182157083_6919652085810069504_n-1627-1807.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft&nbsp;su\u00fdt c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</span>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3 1-2 v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ec7ch c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 khi b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video Quang Hai mo ti so cho Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Video Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/video-quang-hai-mo-ti-so-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty song tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i SEA Games 29, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecfng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn U22 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o HAGL v\u1eabn c\u00f3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng chu\u1ed9c t\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c l\u00ean t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 3-0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o gi\u00fap C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Video Cong Phuong bo lo 2 qua penalty cho Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Video C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/clip-cong-phuong-bo-lo-2-qua-penalty-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Truong dinh chan thuong trong tran dau voi Pakistan.\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 do m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 6 b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng \u1edf c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n, bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129. T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c lo ng\u1ea1i b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do HLV Park Hang Seo x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.&nbsp;Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV \u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau-292-194491.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau-292-194491.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn tin x\u1ea5u: Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed1c Tuy\u00ean Quang v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2373","checkdouble":"194498"},{"date":"21:06 14/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi anh kh\u00f4ng s\u00fat tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang d\u1ed9i ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Paksitan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0\u1eddng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 khao kh\u00e1t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao. H\u00f4m nay, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 ghi b\u00e0n hay kh\u00f4ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y. Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u1ea5y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng qu\u00ean \u0111i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal trong 2 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV \u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2372","checkdouble":"194499"},{"date":"21:25 14/08","title":"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo1534244610614-1534244610614227491263.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 penalty\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 11m n\u1eefa\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u00e0o trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Iraq, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Qatar.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2371","checkdouble":"194500"},{"date":"22:40 14/08","title":"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n do ch\u00ednh anh v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, chuy\u00ean gia Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf n\u00f3i tr\u00ean VTC News: \"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00e2m l\u00fd. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi 17, 18 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1ef3, nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng m\u00e3i v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nhau. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 - chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, song c\u1ee9 ra s\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00f4i\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh CLB SLNA H\u1ed3 V\u0103n Chi\u00eam l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u00fd (HLV Park Hang Seo) cho Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u1eea, th\u00ec c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 tinh t\u1ebf l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Thi\u1ebfu g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u201cN\u00f3\u201d - l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. \u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng hai l\u1ea7n. Kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1, kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, BHL Quang Huy l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede ch\u1ea5m 11 m, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 si\u00eau sao n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng t\u1eebng s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Diego Maradona, Michel Platini \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau, c\u00f2n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. \u00d4ng Park r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, do \u0111\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, BHL Quang Huy cho bi\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +3, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/8, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nepal l\u00fac 19h00, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16.5pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2370","checkdouble":"194501"},{"date":"22:23 14/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/8: M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Leroy Sane \u201cphi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-148-mu-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-leroy-sane-phien-ban-20.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u201csao mai\u201d Bundesliga, Real t\u00ednh mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea, PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Eriksen,\u2026 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 14/8.</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eafm \u201csao mai\u201d Bundesliga</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Man United \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb Linton Maina, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Hannover 96. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Man Utd sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, theo Sportbuzzer. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U-19 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Leroy Sane m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 148 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 148 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/linton-maina-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Linton Maina (tr\u00e1i)</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Don Balon, CLB Real Madrid s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf cho Marcelo trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 hay, Alonso c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Real \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Man Utd t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n De Gea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd BBC\u00a0ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\" r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n David De Gea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man Utd nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng trong chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>PSG g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua Eriksen<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin PSG \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua Christian Eriksen t\u1eeb Tottenham. \u0110\u00e2y la\u0300 \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng tha\u0301i kh\u00f4ng qua\u0301 b\u00e2\u0301t ng\u01a1\u0300 trong b\u00f4\u0301i ca\u0309nh Adrien Rabiot \u0111a\u0301nh ti\u00ea\u0301ng mu\u00f4\u0301n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Eriksen v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi H\u00e8 2020. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 PSH h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Salah mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal khi anh kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Unai Emery, sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i\u00a0Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Mateo Guendouzi.\u00a0Mohamed Elneny mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Milan mua sao x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 hai CLB c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 Italy \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tiemoue Bakayoko. AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.\u00a0C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u c\u1ee7a Milan m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, sau Pepe Reina, Ivan Strinic, Mattia Caldara, Samu Castillejo, v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain.</p>\r\n<h2>Herrera b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrerra d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man Utd. \"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i cho Manchester United. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho CLB. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, C\u0110V n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t vui.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ghi nh\u1edb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m v\u1edbi CLB. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u , t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 160 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 200 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n cho CLB\".</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">XEM TH\u00caM:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-mu-sap-hoan-tat-ban-hop-dong-trong-mo-184-194435.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8: M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2369","checkdouble":"194502"},{"date":"23:00 14/08","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo1534244610614-1534244610614227491263.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 penalty\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 11m n\u1eefa\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u00e0o trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Iraq, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Qatar.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2368","checkdouble":"194504"},{"date":"23:17 14/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo-9-15342012338401446270955.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u00e2p v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m, s\u00e1ng mai (15/8), Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 l\u00fac 10h30. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1ebd t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xa kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n, thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Samsung hay di chuy\u1ec3n g\u1ea7n 50 km t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp do Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i ASIAD. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, do s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Samsung kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n n\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp trong s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u00e2n m\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2367","checkdouble":"194505"},{"date":"06:26 15/08","title":"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-lopetegui-muon-no-bom-tan-bld-real-noi-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung phong, nh\u01b0ng Real ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd AS, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Real cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean ''\u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3'' sau v\u1ee5 PSG mua Neymar n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 Chelsea mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lo2-4997-1534216722.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lopetegui b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, tr\u1eeb khi Real mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao. \u1ea2nh: Reuters</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Vinicius v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Real m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh trong h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Courtois ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la, ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung phong v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Rea kh\u00f3 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1ea5t trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua. Trong khi Karim Benzema c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Borja Mayoral. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Real. Bayern ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 Robert Lewandowski, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Jesus Vallejo hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, trong khi Sergio Ramos, Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Nacho c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd AS, v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m, Real \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 mua Neymar. Kylian Mbappe c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2366","checkdouble":"194507"},{"date":"06:46 15/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Monchi, AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 AS Roma m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 26.65 tri\u1ec7u euro. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Giallorossi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed b\u1ed5 sung 4 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1eadm \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi, b\u1edfi Nzonzi nguy\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u01a1i G\u0110 Monchi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Nzonzi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 ba m\u00f9a thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi AS Roma nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 42.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nzonzi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 5 trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Les Bleus t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma, Nzonzi cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Roma. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong vi\u1ec7c AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi, G\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi cho bi\u1ebft: \"Nzonzi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nzonzi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u